#: course/lesson-6-multiple-function-parameters/lesson.tres:14
msgid ""
"In the previous lesson, you created a function to draw a square of a fixed size."
msgstr "在上一部分中，你创建了一个函数来绘制一个固定大小的正方形。"

msgid ""
"This function is a bit limiting. Instead, it would be much better if we "
"had a function to draw a square of [i]any[/i] size. Or better: any kind "
"of rectangle (a square is a specific kind of rectangle)."
msgstr ""
"这个功能有点限制。 相反，如果我们有一个函数来绘制一个 [i]任意[/i] 大小的正方形会更好。 "
"或者更好的是：任何类型的矩形（正方形是特殊的矩形）。"

msgid ""
"In previous lessons, you used the [code]rotate()[/code] function and gave it an [b]argument[/b]."
msgstr "在之前的课程中，你使用了 [code]rotate()[/code] 函数并给了它一个 [b]参数[/b]。"

#: course/lesson-6-multiple-function-parameters/lesson.tres:38
msgid ""
"Just like [code]rotate()[/code], we can also give our functions [b]parameters[/b]."
msgstr ""
"就像 [code]rotate()[/code] 一样，我们也可以给我们的函数定义 [b]参数[/b]。"

msgid ""
"Parameters act as [i]placeholders[/i] in the function's code. They work "
"like blank spaces that get filled in each time someone calls your function."
msgstr ""
"参数在函数代码中充当 [i]占位符[/i]。他们就像是空白格，每次调用函数时都会被填入具体的内容。"

msgid ""
"When you write a function with parameters, you create a flexible template that can work with different values each time you use it. Let's see how the rotate() function is defined and uses a parameter:"
msgstr ""
"当你编写带函数的参数时，你实际上是在创建一个灵活的模板，每次使用时都可以处理不同的值。让我们看看 rotate() 是如何定义和使用参数的。"

#: course/lesson-6-multiple-function-parameters/lesson.tres:62
msgid ""
"For now, focus on the first line, the function [i]definition[/i]: [code]func rotate(radians)[/code]."
msgstr "现在，请关注第一行 [i]定义[/i]：[code]func rotate(radians)[/code]。"

msgid ""
"The word [code]radians[/code] is the function's parameter. It's the placeholder that gets \"replaced\" with the actual value when you call the function."
msgstr ""
" "[code]radians[/code]" 是一个占位符，当你调用函数时，会被实际值替换。"

msgid ""
"When you [i]call[/i] this function with [code]rotate(0.5)[/code], the computer replaces the name "
"\"radians\" in the function with [code]0.5[/code]."
msgstr ""
"当你[i]调用[/i] [code]rotate(0.5)[/code] 时，计算机会将值 [code]0.5[/code] 绑定到标签 "
"[code]radians[/code]。"

msgid ""
"Wherever the computer sees the identifier [code]radians[/code] inside the"
" function, it replaces it with the [code]0.5[/code] value."
msgstr "计算机在函数内任何地方看到标识符 [code]radians[/code]，都会将其替换为 [code]0.5[/code] 。"

msgid ""
"Each time you call the function, the replacement happens again: "
"If you call [code]rotate(1.2)[/code], [code]radians[/code] becomes [code]1.2[/code]."
msgstr ""
"每次调用函数时，就会再次进行替换："
"如果你调用 [code]rotate(1.2)[/code]，[code]radians[/code] 就会变成 [code]1.2[/code]。"

msgid ""
"The parameter can be filled with a number, text, or anything else. "
"In this lesson, we'll only use numbers as we have yet to learn about other value types."
msgstr ""
"参数可以被数字、文本或者其他内容来填充。"
"在本节课中，我们将只使用数字，因为我们还没有学习其他值类型。"

#: course/lesson-6-multiple-function-parameters/lesson.tres:78
msgid "What is a function parameter?"
msgstr "什么是函数参数？"

#: course/lesson-6-multiple-function-parameters/lesson.tres:81
msgid "A parameter is a placeholder that gets replaced with the actual value you pass when calling the function."
msgstr "参数是一个占位符，在调用函数时，它会被你传入的实际值替换。"

msgid ""
"The value can be different each time you call the function: "
"it depends on what you put in parentheses."
msgstr "调用时值可能会改变：这取决于你在调用函数时放入括号中的内容。"

#: course/lesson-6-multiple-function-parameters/lesson.tres:84
msgid "A label you give to a value the function receives."
msgstr "你为函数接收的值赋予的标签。"

#: course/lesson-6-multiple-function-parameters/lesson.tres:84
msgid "A number you use to make calculations."
msgstr "用于计算的数字。"

#: course/lesson-6-multiple-function-parameters/lesson.tres:84
msgid "The name of a function."
msgstr "函数的名称。"

#: course/lesson-6-multiple-function-parameters/lesson.tres:92
msgid "How to create functions with parameters"
msgstr "如何创建带参数的函数"

#: course/lesson-6-multiple-function-parameters/lesson.tres:94
msgid ""
"When you write a function [i]definition[/i] "
"(the line starting with the [code]func[/code] keyword), you can add parameters."
msgstr ""
"编写函数 [i]定义[/i]（即以 [code]func[/code] 关键字开头的那一行）时，你可以添加参数。"

msgid ""
"To add a parameter, write a placeholder name inside the parentheses. "
"When someone calls your function with a value, "
"every copy of the parameter in the function gets replaced with that value."
msgstr ""
"要添加参数，请在括号内写入一个占位符名称。当调用你的函数并传入数值时，函数内该参数都会被替换为那个数值。"

#: course/lesson-6-multiple-function-parameters/lesson.tres:116
msgid ""
"You can give parameters any name! How you name functions and parameters "
"is up to you."
msgstr "你可以为参数指定任何名称，如何命名函数和参数取决于你。"

msgid ""
"Just remember that names cannot contain spaces. To write parameter names "
"with multiple words, in GDScript, we use underscores by convention."
msgstr "只不过要留意，名称不能包含空格。 如果要在一个名称里用到多个单词，在 GDScript 中，你需要使用下划线分隔。"

msgid ""
"The following function definition is exactly equivalent to the previous "
"one."
msgstr "下面的函数定义与上一个完全等价。"

#: course/lesson-6-multiple-function-parameters/lesson.tres:140
msgid ""
"Parameters make your code easier to reuse. "
"You write the function once as a template, then you can call it many times with different values."
msgstr ""
"参数使你的代码更易于重复使用。"
"你只需要编写一次函数作为模板，之后便可用不同的值反复调用。"

msgid ""
"Here's an example with a function to draw any square. "
"The parameter [code]size[/code] is a placeholder. "
"Use the slider to change the value. "
"When you click the button, the app calls [code]draw_square()[/code] and the placeholder gets replaced with your value, "
"drawing squares of different sizes."
msgstr ""
"这里有一个绘制任意正方形的函数示例，参数 [code]size[/code] 是一个占位符。"
"请使用滑块更改数值，当你点击按钮时，应用会调用 [code]draw_square()[/code]，"
"占位符会被替换为你设定的数值，从而绘制出不同的大小的正方形。"

#: course/lesson-6-multiple-function-parameters/lesson.tres:156
msgid "Which is the correct syntax for a function definition?"
msgstr "下列哪个函数定义的语法是正确的？"

#: course/lesson-6-multiple-function-parameters/lesson.tres:159
msgid ""
"To define a function, you need to start with the [code]func[/code] "
"keyword followed by a space, the [code]function_name[/code], and optional"
" parameters inside parentheses."
msgstr ""
"要定义一个函数，你需要以 [code]func[/code] 关键字开头，后跟一个空格、[code]function_name[/code] "
"和括号内的可选参数。"

msgid ""
"You must end the line with a colon, which defines a new code block. We'll"
" see moving forward that keywords other than [code]func[/code] require a "
"colon at the end of the line."
msgstr "你必须以冒号结束该行，它定义了一个新的代码块。 之后我们还会看到 [code]func[/code] 以外的关键字也需要在行尾用冒号。"

#: course/lesson-6-multiple-function-parameters/lesson.tres:162
#: course/lesson-6-multiple-function-parameters/lesson.tres:163
msgid "func function_name(parameter_name):"
msgstr "func function_name(parameter_name):"

#: course/lesson-6-multiple-function-parameters/lesson.tres:162
msgid "func (function_name): parameter_name"
msgstr "func (function_name): parameter_name"

#: course/lesson-6-multiple-function-parameters/lesson.tres:162
msgid "func function_name(parameter_name)"
msgstr "func function_name(parameter_name)"

#: course/lesson-6-multiple-function-parameters/lesson.tres:162
msgid "function_name(parameter_name):"
msgstr "function_name(parameter_name):"

#: course/lesson-6-multiple-function-parameters/lesson.tres:174
msgid "Functions can have multiple parameters"
msgstr "函数可以有多个参数"

#: course/lesson-6-multiple-function-parameters/lesson.tres:176
msgid ""
"A function can have multiple parameters. "
"You can use as many placeholders as you [i]need[/i]."
msgstr "一个函数可以拥有多个参数。根据你的 [i] 需要 [/i]，可以使用任意数量的占位符。"

msgid ""
"To add multiple parameters, write a comma between each placeholder name."
msgstr "要添加多个参数，请在每个占位符名称之间添加一个逗号。"

msgid ""
"For example, [code]func move(x, y)[/code] has two placeholders: "
"[code]x[/code] and [code]y[/code]. Each one gets replaced with "
"its own value when you call the function."
msgstr ""
"例如，[code]func move(x, y)[/code] 有两个占位符：[code]x[/code] 和 "
"[code]y[/code]。当你调用函数时，每一个占位符都会被替换为各自对应的数值。"

#: course/lesson-6-multiple-function-parameters/lesson.tres:198
msgid "Must I write spaces between function parameters?"
msgstr "函数参数之间必须加空格吗？"

#: course/lesson-6-multiple-function-parameters/lesson.tres:200
msgid ""
"In a function definition, you must have a space between the "
"[code]func[/code] keyword and the function name."
msgstr "在函数定义中，[code]func[/code] 关键字和函数名之间必须有一个空格。"

msgid ""
"However, because we use the comma to separate parameters, it doesn't "
"matter if you use spaces between parameters. As long as you have the "
"comma, either syntax is correct."
msgstr "但是，因为我们已经有逗号分隔参数，所以参数之间是否加空格无关紧要。 只要你有逗号，加不加额外的空格都是正确的。"

msgid "We often use spaces after the comma for readability."
msgstr "为了便于阅读，我们才经常在逗号后使用空格。"

#: course/lesson-6-multiple-function-parameters/lesson.tres:214
msgid ""
"The following example shows a function with two parameters. "
"The function moves an entity on both the X and Y axes."
msgstr "以下示例定义了一个函数，该函数使用两个参数在 X 轴和 Y 轴上移动实体。"

msgid ""
"When you call [code]move(50, 100)[/code], every [code]x[/code] "
"in the function gets replaced with [code]50[/code], and every "
"[code]y[/code] gets replaced with [code]100[/code]."
msgstr ""
"当你调用 [code]move(50,100)[/code] 时，函数内所有的 [code]x[/code] "
"都会被替换为[code]50[/code]，而所有的 [code]y[/code] 都会被替换为 [code]y[/code]"

#: course/lesson-6-multiple-function-parameters/lesson.tres:234
msgid "How should I name my functions and parameters?"
msgstr "我应该如何命名我的函数和参数？"

#: course/lesson-6-multiple-function-parameters/lesson.tres:236
msgid ""
"The names of functions, parameters, or other things in your code are "
"entirely up to you."
msgstr "代码中的函数、参数或其他内容的名称完全取决于你。"

msgid ""
"They are written by us programmers for other programmers. You want to use"
" the names that make the most sense to you and fellow programmers."
msgstr "它们是我们作为程序员为其他程序员写的。你应该使用你和你的同事都最容易看懂的名称。"

msgid ""
"You could absolutely write single-letter names like in maths classes: "
"[code]a[/code], [code]b[/code], [code]f[/code]."
msgstr "你确实可以像上数学课那样只用一个字母的名称：[code]a[/code]、[code]b[/code]、[code]f[/code]。"

msgid ""
"You can also write abbreviated names like [code]pos[/code] for position, "
"[code]bg[/code] for background, and so on."
msgstr ""
"你还可以写缩写名称，例如 [code]pos[/code] 表示位置（posiotion），[code]bg[/code] "
"表示背景（background），等等。"

msgid "Many programmers do either or both of the above."
msgstr "许多程序员都或多或少会用到上面这两种方式。"

msgid "At GDQuest, we favor complete and explicit names."
msgstr "在 GDQuest课程里，我们倾向于完整和明确的名称。"

msgid ""
"We generally try to write code that is explicit and relatively easy to "
"read."
msgstr "我们应该时刻努力写出明确且相对容易阅读的代码。"

msgid ""
"Right now, you have to enter every letter when you code, so long names "
"may feel inconvenient."
msgstr "现在，你必须在编码时输入每个字母，因此长名称可能会让人感到不便。"

msgid ""
"However, this is good for learning: it trains your fingers to "
"[ignore]type precisely."
msgstr "但是，这对学习有好处：它可以训练你的手指打字做到随心所欲。"

msgid ""
"Then, after you finish this course, you will see that the computer "
"assists you a lot when you code real games with a feature called auto-"
"completion."
msgstr "然后，在你完成本课程后，你会发现当你实际编写游戏时，计算机会使用一种称为自动补全的功能协助你。"

msgid ""
"Based on a few characters you [ignore]type, it will offer you to complete"
" long names."
msgstr "根据你键入的几个字符，它会为你补完完整的长名称。"

#: course/lesson-6-multiple-function-parameters/lesson.tres:256
msgid "When defining a function, parameters are..."
msgstr "定义函数时，参数是..."

#: course/lesson-6-multiple-function-parameters/lesson.tres:259
msgid ""
"You can define functions with or without parameters, depending on your "
"needs."
msgstr "定义函数可带参数可不带，这取决于你的需求。"

#: course/lesson-6-multiple-function-parameters/lesson.tres:268
msgid "Optional"
msgstr "可选"

#: course/lesson-6-multiple-function-parameters/lesson.tres:268
msgid "Mandatory"
msgstr "硬性要求"

#: course/lesson-6-multiple-function-parameters/lesson.tres:276
msgid "What's the correct syntax to define a function with multiple parameters?"
msgstr "定义具有多个参数的函数的正确语法是什么？"

#: course/lesson-6-multiple-function-parameters/lesson.tres:279
msgid ""
"You always write the function parameters inside of the parentheses. To "
"define multiple parameters, you separate them with a comma."
msgstr "你始终得将函数参数写在括号内。 要定义多个参数，请用逗号分隔它们。"

#: course/lesson-6-multiple-function-parameters/lesson.tres:280
msgid "func function_name(parameter_1, parameter_2, ...):"
msgstr "func 函数名(参数_1, 参数_2, ...):"

#: course/lesson-6-multiple-function-parameters/lesson.tres:280
msgid "func function_name(parameter_1 parameter_2 ...):"
msgstr "func 函数名(参数_1 参数_2 ...):"

#: course/lesson-6-multiple-function-parameters/lesson.tres:280
msgid "func function_name(): parameter_1, parameter_2, ..."
msgstr "func 函数名(): 参数_1, 参数_2, ..."

#: course/lesson-6-multiple-function-parameters/lesson.tres:290
msgid ""
"Now it's your turn to create a function with multiple parameters."
msgstr "现在轮到你来创建一个多参数的函数了。"

msgid ""
"In the following practices, you'll write functions that I will call with "
"different values. Your functions need to work correctly no matter what values "
"the app passes to them."
msgstr ""
"在接下来的练习中，你需要编写一些函数，我会用不同的值来调用它们。无论应用传入什么值，"
"你的函数都必须能正常运行。"

#: course/lesson-6-multiple-function-parameters/lesson.tres:300
msgid "Drawing corners of different sizes"
msgstr "绘制不同大小的角"

#: course/lesson-6-multiple-function-parameters/lesson.tres:301
msgid ""
"Before we create a rectangle of any size, let's first practice with a simpler shape."
msgstr "在我们创建任意大小的矩形之前，让我们先看看如何使用参数来绘制更简单的形状。"

msgid
"I will call your function twice with different values:"
msgstr "我会用不同的数值调用你的函数两次："

msgid ""
"Your task is to add a parameter named [code]length[/code] to your function definition. "
"This creates a placeholder. When the app calls your function, the placeholder will get "
"replaced with the value in parentheses."
msgstr ""
"在函数定义中添加一个名为 [code]length[/code] 的参数。这就创建了一个占位符。"
"当应用调用函数时，这个占位符会被替换成括号里的数值。"

msgid ""
"Your function should move the turtle forward by an amount defined by the "
"[code]length[/code] parameter, turn right [code]90[/code] degrees, then move "
"forward by [code]length[/code] again."
msgstr ""
"你的函数应该使海龟向前移动一个由参数 [code]length[/code] 定义的量，向右转动 "
"[code]90[/code] 度，然后向前移动 [code]length[/code] 个像素。"

msgid ""
"Each time the app calls your function, [code]length[/code] will be replaced "
"with a different value: first [code]240[/code], then [code]120[/code]."
msgstr ""
"每次应用调用函数时，[code]length[/code] 都会被替换成不同的值：先是"
"[code]240[/code]，然后是 [code]120[/code]。"

#: course/lesson-6-multiple-function-parameters/lesson.tres:319
msgid ""
"You need to add the parameter [code]length[/code] three times in this practice"
msgstr "在这个练习中，你需要添加三次 [code]length[/code] 参数。"

#: course/lesson-6-multiple-function-parameters/lesson.tres:325
msgid ""
"Using function parameters, code a function you can reuse to draw corners "
"with lines of varying sizes."
msgstr "使用函数参数，编写一个可以重复使用的函数，绘制边长不同的角。"

#: course/lesson-6-multiple-function-parameters/lesson.tres:330
msgid "Using multiple parameters"
msgstr "使用多个参数"

#: course/lesson-6-multiple-function-parameters/lesson.tres:331
msgid ""
"Now let's make the [code]draw_corner()[/code] function even more flexible. "
"We'll add a second placeholder so the angle can also vary."
msgstr ""
"现在，让我们让 [code]draw_corner[/code] 函数变得更加灵活。"
"我们将添加第二个占位符，这样角度也可以改变。"

msgid ""
"I will call your function with different length and angle values:"
msgstr "我会用不同的长度和角度来调用不同的函数："

msgid ""
"Your task is to add the [code]angle[/code] parameter after [code]length[/code] "
"in the function definition. Remember to separate the two placeholders with a comma."
msgstr ""
"在函数中，将 [code]angle[/code] 参数添加到 [code]length[/code] 之后，"
"记得用逗号分隔这两个占位符。"

msgid ""
"Remember: When the app calls [code]draw_corner(240, 45)[/code], the parameter "
"[code]length[/code] will get replaced with [code]240[/code] and [code]angle[/code] "
"will get replaced with [code]45[/code]."
msgstr ""
"记住，当应用调用 [code]draw_corner(240,45)[/code] 时，参数 [code]length[/code]，会被"
"会被替换成 [code]240[/code]，而 [code]angle[/code] 会被替换成 [code]45[/code]。"

#: course/lesson-6-multiple-function-parameters/lesson.tres:353
msgid "With two parameters, code a function to draw corners with any angle."
msgstr "使用两个参数，编写一个函数来绘制任意角度的角。"

#: course/lesson-6-multiple-function-parameters/lesson.tres:358
msgid "Drawing squares of any size"
msgstr "绘制任意大小的正方形"

#: course/lesson-6-multiple-function-parameters/lesson.tres:359
msgid ""
"Time to write a complete function from scratch! You'll make a function "
"that draws squares of any size."
msgstr ""
"是时候从头开始编写一个完整的函数了！你将编写一个能绘制任意大小正方形的函数。"

msgid "I will call your function with different sizes:"
msgstr "我会用不同的大小值来调用你的函数："

msgid ""
"Write a function named [code]draw_square()[/code] with one parameter called "
"[code]length[/code]. Remember, this parameter is a placeholder that gets filled "
"with the actual value when the function is called."
msgstr ""
"编写一个名为 [code]draw_square()[/code] 的函数，并包含一个名为 [code]length[/code] 的参数。"
"记住，这个参数是一个占位符，当函数被调用时，它会被填入实际的数值。"


msgid ""
"Create a function named [code]draw_square()[/code] that takes one "
"parameter: the [code]length[/code] of the square's sides."
msgstr "创建一个名为 [code]draw_square()[/code] 的函数，它有一个参数："
"正方形边的 [code]length[/code]。"

msgid ""
"Your function needs to move forward by [code]length[/code], turn right "
"90 degrees, and do this four times to complete all four sides of the square."
msgstr ""
"你的函数需要向前移动 [code]length[/code] 的距离，向右转 90 度，并将此过程重复四次，"
"以画完正方形的全部四条边。"

msgid ""
"[b]Important:[/b] When the turtle finishes drawing, it should face right. "
"So you need to turn right a total of four times."
msgstr ""
"[b]重要提示：[/b]当乌龟画完时，它应该朝向右侧。所以你总共需要向右转四次。"

#: course/lesson-6-multiple-function-parameters/lesson.tres:380
msgid ""
"In the previous lesson, your function would draw squares of a fixed size."
" Using a parameter, code a function to draw squares of any size."
msgstr "在上一课中，你的函数能够绘制固定大小的正方形。通过增加一个参数，编写一个函数来绘制任意大小的正方形。"

#: course/lesson-6-multiple-function-parameters/lesson.tres:385
msgid "Drawing rectangles of any size"
msgstr "绘制任意大小的矩形"

#: course/lesson-6-multiple-function-parameters/lesson.tres:386
msgid "Let's create a function to draw rectangles with any length and height."
msgstr "让我们创建一个函数，用来绘制任意长和高的矩形。"

msgid "I will call your function twice with different sizes:"
msgstr "我会用不同的大小调用你的函数两次："

msgid ""
"Your function needs two parameters: [code]length[/code] and [code]height[/code]. "
"When the app calls your function, the first number replaces [code]length[/code], "
"and the second number replaces [code]height[/code]."
msgstr ""
"你的函数需要两个参数：[code]length[/code] 和 [code]height[/code]。"
"当应用调用函数时，第一个数值会替换 [code]length[/code]，而另一个会替换 [code]height[/code]。"

msgid "Use [code]length[/code] when you move horizontally and [code]height[/code] when you move vertically."
msgstr "水平移动时请使用 [code]length[/code]，垂直移动请使用 [code]height[/code]。"

msgid ""
"This is the pattern you need to follow: move forward by [code]length[/code], turn right, move forward by "
"[code]height[/code], turn right, then repeat this sequence once more."
msgstr "你需要遵循这个模式：向前移动 [code]length[/code] 的距离，向右转，"
"然后再重复一次这个过程。"

msgid ""
"[b]Important:[/b] When the turtle finishes drawing, it should face right. "
"Make sure you turn right four times in total."
msgstr "[b]重要提示：[/b]当乌龟画完时，它应该朝向右侧。请确保你总共右转了四次。"

#: course/lesson-6-multiple-function-parameters/lesson.tres:411
msgid "You need to specify the two parameters in the function definition"
msgstr "你需要在函数中定义中指定这两个参数"

msgid "Use [code]func draw_rectangle(length, height):[/code]"
msgstr "请使用 [code]func draw_rectangle(length, height):[/code]"

msgid ""
"When calling move_forward, you need to alternate between using the length "
"and the height arguments when calling move_forward."
msgstr "在调用 move_forward 时，你需要交替使用 length 和 height 参数。"

#: course/lesson-6-multiple-function-parameters/lesson.tres:381
msgid ""
"With one parameter, you can make squares of any size. With two, you can "
"draw any rectangle! You'll do so in this practice."
msgstr "使用一个参数，你可以制作任意大小的正方形。 有了两个，你可以绘制任何矩形！ 你将在本练习中这样做。"

#: course/lesson-6-multiple-function-parameters/lesson.tres:385
msgid "Your First Function Parameter"
msgstr "你的第一个函数参数"
